Maria a 20 year old, orphanage tried of surviving in this hectic world. 
Leaving for a vacation in maldives, with all what she had saved in the past 1 year she booked a villa.
But her stay was not going to be what she expected.
That day when she arrived, she started to heasr certain weird noises and someone screaching on the bathroom door.
Maria was in histerics, and crept against the wall.
she screamed! but no one was to help, began to pray to god, and suddenly out of know where,
A cameraman stood up and begin to record everything! jake stood and told Maria that it was a live show that 
scares people on their trips and telecasts their reaction. Maria was in rage and slaped the door on their faces.
Deep in her heart, she was scared but still enjoyed the rest of her stay.